<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 01:52:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巨型鱿鱼的发现揭示了澳大利亚附近隐藏的深海世界</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/giant-squid-discovery-uncovers-a-hidden-deep-sea-world-off-australia</link><description>科学家们在西澳大利亚海岸探索深水下峡谷时发现了一个隐藏的世界，里面充满了奇异而难以捉摸的海洋生物，其中包括传说中的巨型乌贼的踪迹。通过分析 4 公里以上海水中漂浮的 DNA 痕迹，研究人员发现了 226 个物种，从深潜鲸鱼到该地区罕见或从未见过的奇怪鱼类。有些生物甚至可能不为科学所知。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/giant-squid-discovery-uncovers-a-hidden-deep-sea-world-off-australia.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 01:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/giant-squid-discovery-uncovers-a-hidden-deep-sea-world-off-australia</guid></item><item><title>人工智能设计简化量子电路计算</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-designs-simplify-quantum-circuit-calculations</link><description>用于复杂量子计算的电路通常受到其尺寸和复杂性的限制。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-designs-simplify-quantum-circuit-calculations.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 01:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-designs-simplify-quantum-circuit-calculations</guid></item><item><title>Intuitive Machines 收购地面站公司</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/intuitive-machines-to-buy-ground-station-company</link><description>华盛顿——Intuitive Machines 已同意收购一家在美国和英国运营地面站的公司，以帮助建设月球通信网络。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/intuitive-machines-to-buy-ground-station-company2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 01:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/intuitive-machines-to-buy-ground-station-company</guid></item><item><title>实验室培养的大脑可以玩电子游戏</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-lab-grown-brain-that-can-play-video-games</link><description>科学家希望由活细胞制成的计算机能够解开多动症和精神分裂症的病因&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-lab-grown-brain-that-can-play-video-games.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 01:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-lab-grown-brain-that-can-play-video-games</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部要求苹果和谷歌识别该汽车应用程序的超过 100,000 名用户</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-doj-is-demanding-apple-and-google-identify-over-100000-users-of-this-car-app</link><description>EZ Lynk 律师在信中写道，苹果和谷歌正计划对传票进行抗辩。沃尔玛拒绝置评。其他被传唤的公司均未回应置评请求。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-doj-is-demanding-apple-and-google-identify-over-100000-users-of-this-car-app.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 00:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-doj-is-demanding-apple-and-google-identify-over-100000-users-of-this-car-app</guid></item><item><title>低成本3D打印机可以通过超薄光控薄膜获得医疗级精度</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/low-cost-3d-printers-could-gain-medical-grade-precision-from-ultrathin-light-control-film</link><description>研究人员开发出了一种超薄光学薄膜，可以提高 LCD 树脂 3D 打印机中使用的光线质量。这一进步有助于确保微小细节的精确复制，从而可以以更低的成本 3D 打印医疗级或工业级产品。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/low-cost-3d-printers-could-gain-medical-grade-precision-from-ultrathin-light-control-film2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 00:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/low-cost-3d-printers-could-gain-medical-grade-precision-from-ultrathin-light-control-film</guid></item><item><title>使用混合干细胞产品进行脐带血移植，白血病患者的存活率为 96%，且无 GVHD</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/umbilical-cord-blood-transplant-with-pooled-stem-cell-product-shows-96-survival-and-no-gvhd-in-leukemia-patients</link><description>一种使用脐带血治疗血液疾病的新方法可以使需要干细胞移植的患者更容易获得治疗。一项对接受脐带血移植加上来自混合脐带血单位的干细胞产品的患者进行的 II 期临床试验表明，28 名患有白血病和 GVHD 的患者中有 27 名 (96%) 存活了至少一年，并且没有患者出现严重的急性或慢性移植物抗宿主病，这是干细胞移植的常见并发症。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/umbilical-cord-blood-transplant-with-pooled-stem-cell-product-shows-96-survival-and-no-gvhd-in-leukemia-patients2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 00:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/umbilical-cord-blood-transplant-with-pooled-stem-cell-product-shows-96-survival-and-no-gvhd-in-leukemia-patients</guid></item><item><title>CellXpress.ai 系统</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cellxpress-ai-system</link><description>具有集成培养箱、液体处理器和成像仪的革命性系统，可自动执行要求严格的饲喂和传代计划。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cellxpress-ai-system2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 May 2026 00:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cellxpress-ai-system</guid></item><item><title>新量子算法在几秒钟内解决“不可能”的材料问题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-quantum-algorithm-solves-impossible-materials-problem-in-seconds</link><description>一种受量子启发的新算法解决了一个传统超级计算机甚至难以解决的巨大问题。研究人员使用该方法模拟了极其复杂的量子材料（称为准晶体），为强大的新型量子设备和超高效电子产品打开了大门。这项工作可以帮助科学家为未来的量子计算机设计先进的拓扑量子位和材料。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-quantum-algorithm-solves-impossible-materials-problem-in-seconds.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 23:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-quantum-algorithm-solves-impossible-materials-problem-in-seconds</guid></item><item><title>缩小动物运动和机器人控制之间的差距</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/closing-the-gap-between-animal-movement-and-robotic-control</link><description>动物的移动精度和适应性是机器人难以比拟的。卡内基梅隆大学机械工程系的研究人员正在开发一种新的人工智能驱动方法，以揭示大脑和身体如何协同工作。通过将复杂的生物系统转变为可以测试和改进的模型，该团队试图了解和复制机器人系统中的动物表现。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/closing-the-gap-between-animal-movement-and-robotic-control.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 23:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/closing-the-gap-between-animal-movement-and-robotic-control</guid></item></channel></rss>